personalInfo.residence: Knoxville, TN; plays out of Fox Den CC

tourBios.otherInfo: Member of BUY.COM TOUR in 1995-96 and 1998...member of PGA TOUR in 1993 and 1997-98...played in two BUY.COM TOUR events in 1999 as a non-member...finished 19th on the BUY.COM TOUR money list in 1996 with $85,824, his career-best finish...earned second place at 1996 Cleveland Open by finishing one stroke behind Greg Twiggs...was in lead or within one shot of lead at the end of each round of that tournament...fired a final-round 65 to tie for second at the 1996 Wichita Open, one shot behind Rick Cramer...used a 62 in the final round of the 1997 Quad City Classic to tie for second, his career-best PGA TOUR finish...second-team All-America selection in 1992, the same year he won the NCAA East Regional...All-Atlantic Coast Conference selection in 1992...college teammates included David Duval, Charlie Rymer and Tom Shaw...has had seven competitive holes-in-one in his career...mother got him started playing golf.

dyn.dynResults: He has finished 2nd on the Web.com Tour 2 times.
